data.description: 3 or 4 bedroom, 2 bath bilevel in popular Peckville is in a terrific, sought after location.  Needs some cosmetic updating but has excellent bones and a five year old metal roof.  The lower level can be an in law suite with its at grade entry door, bedroom, living room and summer kitchen, so bring Mom or Dad along with you!  Valley View schools and great access to everything in this super location., Baths: 1 Bath Lev 1,1 Bath Lev 2, Beds: 1 Bed LL, SqFt Fin - Main: 1050.00, SqFt Fin - 3rd: 0.00, Tax Information: Available, Dining Area: Y, SqFt Fin - 2nd: 0.00, Additional Info: The fourth bedroom was created in the lower level from what was once a one car garage.  It can be opened back up to again become a garage or use it as it is now, for the bedroom to your inlaw suite, as the downstairs has a kitchen, family room and fulll bath, or for a guest room or a private home office with its own entry.
